creator: Martial Profile Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Martial Profile, the ultimate companion app for martial artists and combat sport enthusiasts. Whether you're a seasoned practitioner or just beginning your martial arts journey, Martial Profile is designed to enhance your experience and take your skills to the next level. Discover the power of this app, your partner in mastering the martial arts world.

Your Martial Arts Hub
With Martial Profile, we've created a hub that caters to every martial discipline, ensuring it's a valuable resource for practitioners across the board. Regardless of whether you excel in the art of Boxing, Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu, Karate, or any other discipline, this app is tailored to suit your unique needs.

Craft Your Martial Identity
Your martial journey is unique, and Martial Profile respects that. Customize your profile by selecting from a range of 18 disciplines and counting. Highlight the arts you practice and showcase your expertise levels, belts, and accomplishments. This is your space to express your martial identity.

Track and Elevate Your Progress
Record your training sessions and monitor your performance effortlessly. Martial Profile empowers you to stay motivated and continually refine your skills. Gain access to comprehensive session analyses and unlock achievements based on your individual profile. It's your personal path to excellence.

Harness the Power of Combat A.I.
Experience the future of martial arts with our innovative Combat A.I. This cutting-edge technology is designed to provide personalized insights and recommendations, helping you evolve your technique and strategy. Martial Profile ensures you keep growing, even beyond the dojo.

Connect with Fellow Martial Artists
Martial Profile fosters connections within the global martial arts community. Join forces with fellow enthusiasts, make friends, and engage in conversations with practitioners who share your passion. Stay updated on local events and take your journey to the next level with your martial arts companions.

Unlock Your True Potential
In martial arts and combat sports, true power emerges from dedication and continuous learning. Martial Profile is your steadfast companion outside the dojo, assisting you on every step of your journey towards excellence.

Constantly Evolving
Our commitment to excellence extends to our app's development. The Martial Profile team is continually working to introduce exciting new features and enhance existing ones. Your experience matters, and we're dedicated to making it better with each update.

Elevate your martial arts journey today with Martial Profile. Download the app and become a part of our vibrant martial arts community. It's time to unleash your full potential and embrace the art of combat. Martial Profile is where champions are made.
descriptionShort: Companion app for martial artists and combat sports. Improve & connect.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
We keep adding more features for our users to improve Martial Profile, this time, we are adding:

- A better and custom on boarding experience
- Leaderboards for each discipline
- Get notified when someone sends you a message
- Improvements for smalls screens

Thanks for being part of the Martial Profile community and keep up the good training!.
